(1) Moderna says RSV vaccine is 84% effective at preventing disease in olde=
r adults [ https://substack.com/redirect/82b05fdd-8722-46b0-a423-badf86f5bc=
7d?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]
Spencer Kimball [ https://substack.com/redirect/462d0326-d4c5-459b-b934-9ac=
